{"tid":2267303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角騷亂酒保認暴動罪 本月23日判刑","createTime":"2020-11-02T03:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T04:06:20.000Z","uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c65de829bdb62ab9ce4cfa915dbce3b2ab6a50","tid":2267303,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【蘋果日報】2016年旺角騷亂多人被起訴，事隔多年至今仍有案件有待審理。其中三名男子面對暴動、刑事毀壞和縱火等罪，今於區域法院審理，早前已表態承認暴動罪的酒保今正式認罪，另有學生承認刑事毀壞，兩人押後至本月23日判刑。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/5ZWX4FQMBBDQ7CRRSK6PWYSBJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F5ZWX4FQMBBDQ7CRRSK6PWYSBJM%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=e873b3c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F5ZWX4FQMBBDQ7CRRSK6PWYSBJM%2F&h=cb922bd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/5ZWX4FQMBBDQ7CRRSK6PWYSBJM/</a>"},{"pid":"a01e86fdbbc1dc8fb4df43871bf6aa21afb9036a","tid":2267303,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f323e016fc9563c7506f49e44ed52fac0341ce4","tid":2267303,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"手足個頭幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e6fb4b2d56cd67a3e63bd9fae7f72b663e6fe1","tid":2267303,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"唉！"},{"pid":"6d460db4ab29e7f08fae6a8354695938b919143f","tid":2267303,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f323e016fc9563c7506f49e44ed52fac0341ce